<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="by-adv">by <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /baɪ/    美 /baɪ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>在近旁；经过：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Don’t stand by.
不要袖手旁观。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A group of children passed by.
一群孩子从旁边过去。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>过去地；已往：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The happy days went by.
那些快乐的日子过去了。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="by-and-by">by and by</h3>
<p>1.<strong>不久以后</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="by-and-large">by and large</h3>
<p>1.<strong>大体上；总体上</strong>  </p></div>